### Test Structure Requirements

All tests must follow the **@testing-rules.mdc** guidelines:

#### Test Organization:
```
tests/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ unit/           # Fast, isolated tests
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ integration/    # Cross-module tests
